name: Dating
body: Through  its  implementation,  this  project  will  familiarize  you  with  the  creation  and  execution  of threads, and with the use of the Thread class methods.  In order to synchronize the threads you will have to use (when necessary), run(), start(),  currentThread(), getName(), join(), yield(), sleep(time), isAlive(), getPriority(), setPriority(), interrupt(), synchronized methods.
